UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The passage discusses a number of ways that the process of "artificial intelligence" is changing the nature of human work. The author focuses on the ways that artificial intelligence is automating tasks that were once performed by humans. The author also points out that artificial intelligence is creating new jobs and opportunities. According to the passage, which of the following statements best describes the author’s view of the impact of artificial intelligence on the future of work?',
